trans-unit.source: Represents the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) <xref uid="langword_csharp_annotation" name="annotation" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Representerar World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) <xref uid="langword_csharp_annotation" name="annotation" href=""> </xref> element.

trans-unit.source: An `annotation` element can contain one or more <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAppInfo> instances (information for applications) and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaDocumentation> instances (comments or text for humans).
trans-unit.target: En `annotation` -element kan innehålla en eller flera <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAppInfo>instanser (information för program) och <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaDocumentation>instanser (kommentarer eller text för människor).</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaDocumentation> </xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAppInfo>

trans-unit.source: An annotation is used to store extra information about the schema or its elements.
trans-unit.target: En anteckning används för att lagra extra information om schemat eller dess element.

trans-unit.source: These notes are specified for human consumption, `xs:documentation`, or by software, `xs:appinfo`.
trans-unit.target: Dessa anmärkningar har angetts för konsumtion `xs:documentation`, eller program, `xs:appinfo`.

trans-unit.source: Annotation can be the first element of most schema elements or anywhere under the schema element.
trans-unit.target: Anteckningen kan vara det första elementet i de flesta schemaelement eller var som helst under schemaelementet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAnnotation"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAnnotation"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the string id.
The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_String.Empty" name="String.Empty" href=""></xref>.

Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Items" name="Items" href=""></xref> collection that is used to store the <xref uid="langword_csharp_appinfo" name="appinfo" href=""></xref> and <xref uid="langword_csharp_documentation" name="documentation" href=""></xref> child elements.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Items" name="Items" href=""> </xref> som används för att lagra den <xref uid="langword_csharp_appinfo" name="appinfo" href=""> </xref> och <xref uid="langword_csharp_documentation" name="documentation" href=""> </xref> underordnade element.

trans-unit.source: An annotation can contain <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAppInfo> (information used by applications) or <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaDocumentation> (comments or text used by humans).
trans-unit.target: En anteckning kan innehålla <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAppInfo>(information som används av program) eller <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaDocumentation>(kommentarer eller text som används av människor).</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaDocumentation> </xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaAppInfo>
